	<div id="content" class="site-content"> 
		<div id="body" class="page-wrapper flex-box bg-car bg-fixed">
		 <div class="page-content">
	 <div class="page-box-1 height-300"> 
		<h1 class="heading-1">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
	<div class="row"> <div class="col-sm-8"> <div class="margin-bottom-regular">
	<h3 class="heading-3 margin-bottom-10">Phổ biến</h3>
	<div class="margin-bottom-small">
	 <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Dịch vụ của chúng tôi là gì? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Đây là dịch vụ sửa chữa xe tại nhà</div> </div> </div> <div class="margin-bottom-small"> 
	 	<div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Cách mà chúng tôi làm việc </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> It's super easy and you don't need to go anywhere, we come to you! Just use our site to tell us what you need done, pick a time and a place, and book your appointment. We will come to your location and perform the service right there. After your service is complete we will process the billing and send you a service report. You can also rate your service experience. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	<div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Cửa hàng đặt ở đâu </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style=""> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Trụ sở chính đặt ở Hà Nội và còn nhiều chi nhánh trên toàn quốc </div> </div> </div>
	 	 <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> What sort of vehicles do you work on? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style=""> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> You drive it? We fix it. Does it have an engine? We're on it, or under it. Well, unless it is electric, diesel or a commercial ride, then we're nowhere near it. We have a huge database of vehicles and every bit of info on them from 1984 to 2016. This lets us connect you and your car with the right mechanic. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	 <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Which cities do you serve? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Wrench is currently available in the following cities: <a href="/cities">Click to view all cities</a> </div> </div> </div>
	 	  <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> What auto repair services do you offer? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style=""> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> We can do over 80% of all car repair and maintenance work can be done outside a shop. Everything from a simple oil and filter change to replacing brake pads and rotors, timing belts, catalytic converters and diagnosing and repairing most ignition, electrical and exhaust problems can be done when and where it's most convenient for you. </div> </div> </div>
	 	   <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Do the mechanics dispose of used filters and oil? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style=""> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> We safely and responsibly handle the removal of all the used oil and filters. </div> </div> </div>
	 	    <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Do you use remanufactured parts? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> We occasionally use remanufactured parts depending on same day part availability. </div> </div> </div> </div>
	 	     <div class="margin-bottom-regular"> <h3 class="heading-3 margin-bottom-10">Service Appointment</h3>
	 	      <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> How do I make an appointment? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> It's quite simple. Go to our website <a href="/">getwrench.com</a>, enter your vehicle information, select the service you need, get your quote, pick a time and service location, enter your payment information and book the appointment. </div> </div> </div>
	 	       <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> What times are available to schedule my appointment? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> It's the modern world - our schedule is your schedule, well, within reason. You will see available appointment times when you book your service. </div> </div> </div>
	 	        <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Can you do same day service? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> If we have openings, we can do Oil Changes and Diagnostics same day. Most other services require one day notice in order to get the parts. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	        <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> How long will it take for my car to be serviced? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> The service time will depend on the work that needs to be done. When you get your quote, it will include the estimated service time for your appointment. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	        <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Where can I get my car serviced? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> You can get your car serviced at the convenience of your home or office. However, due to safety concern for the mechanics, we can't service cars that are parked on the street. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	        <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Is there an additional fee for the mechanic to come to my location? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> There is no additional charge for the mechanic to come to your location. Our motto is Drop the Shop and our motto is free. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	        <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> How can I reschedule an appointment? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Login to your Wrench account and select the CHANGE button on your appointment. Then select a new time and location if needed. We ask that you do so 24 hours in advance if at all possible. </div> </div> </div>
	 	         <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Do you have a cancellation policy? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Yes, there is a $50 fee for cancelling less than 24 hours before your appointment. </div> </div> </div>
	 	          <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> What if the mechanic is late to my appointment? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Our mechanics want to offer you the best experience possible. However, different variables like traffic or unexpected delays from another job can affect their schedule. Our mechanics will try their hardest to keep timely appointments. You will get a text when the mechanic is on their way and you can track their path to arrival. They will contact you directly if they run into delays. If any issues arise please contact us directly at <a href="mailto:hello@getwrench.com">hello@getwrench.com</a>. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	          <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Do I have to be present for the service? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> You will need to give the keys to the mechanic and meet them when they are done. You are welcome to watch but not at all necessary. </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="margin-bottom-regular"> <h3 class="heading-3 margin-bottom-10">Warranty</h3> 
	 	          	<div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Do you have a warranty on your parts and labor? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Yes, our Limited Warranty lasts for 12 months or 12,000 miles after your service is performed. The Warranty Period for oil changes is 90 days or 3,000 miles. If you find that the work or parts provided by Wrench are defective, simply email us at <a href="mailto:hello@getwrench.com">hello@getwrench.com</a> and we will get you scheduled for a warranty review visit. Make sure to check out the complete <a href="/warranty">Wrench Limited Warranty</a> to understand the warranty in detail. </div> </div> </div>
	 	          	 <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> What do I do if something is wrong after my service? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> If you find that the work or parts provided by Wrench are defective, and it's within the Warranty Period of 12 months or 12,000 miles from the service date, then email us at <a href="mailto:hello@getwrench.com">hello@getwrench.com</a> and we will get you scheduled for a warranty review visit. If your service was an oil change, the Warranty Period is 90 days or 3,000 miles. See the complete <a href="/warranty">Wrench Limited Warranty</a> for more details. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	          	 <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Does Wrench have liability insurance? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> You bet. Wrench carries $1,000,000 in liability insurance. </div> </div> </div> </div> 
	 	          	 <div class="margin-bottom-regular">
	 	          	  <h3 class="heading-3 margin-bottom-10">Payment</h3> 
	 	          	 	<div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> How much does this cost? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display: none;"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> We believe in fair and upfront pricing. That is why we offer fixed quotes. We have instant quotes for some common jobs, just start the process to book an appointment and we will show you the quote. For other services, we will send you a fixed quote for the services you need. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	          	 	<div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Is credit card information required to book an appointment? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display: none;"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Yes, credit card information is required to make an appointment. Your credit card will be pre-authorized when you schedule an appointment, but you will not be charged until your service is completed. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	          	 	<div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> How do I pay for the service? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display: none;"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> You pay for the service using your credit or debit card. You are required to enter your payment information when you book your appointment. Your card will be authorized at the time of booking but will only be charged once the service is complete. </div> </div> </div>
	 	          	 	 <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Where can I find my receipt for my service? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> You will be emailed a copy of the receipt after the service on your vehicle is complete. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	          	 	 <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> How can I resolve my billing issues? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style="display:none"> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Billing should be pretty straight forward, but if you have any questions, drop us a line at <a href="mailto:hello@getwrench.com">hello@getwrench.com</a>. Please provide us your account information when you contact us. </div> </div> </div> </div>
	 	          	 	  <div class="margin-bottom-regular"> <h3 class="heading-3 margin-bottom-10">Mechanics</h3>
	 	          	 	  <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> What types of experience do your mechanics have? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style=""> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Our mechanics have over 5 years of experience. They have worked in shops and have proven track records of great customer service and do quality work. </div> </div> </div> 
	 	          	 	  <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Do you background check Wrench mechanics? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style=""> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> Yes. All of our mechanics have passed a thorough background check. </div> </div> </div>
	 	          	 	   <div class="margin-bottom-small"> <div class="wrench-box-1 link bg-grey faqQuestion"> Am I supposed to tip the mechanic? </div> <div class="animation-wrapper" style=""> <div class="wrench-box-1 wrench-slideFromTop"> No. We pay our mechanics to do quality service every time. The biggest tip they can receive is your rating and feedback you provide on their profile. </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-sm-4"> <div class="heading-3 margin-bottom-10 invisible">Just to take up space</div> 
